<h3>Facilities:</h3>

<p>New Vision University Hospital is a modern, well-equipped facility that is designed to provide the best possible care to patients. The hospital has a total of 150 beds, which are spread across various departments. The hospital has a dedicated emergency department, intensive care unit, neonatal intensive care unit, and a surgery department, among others. The hospital is also equipped with advanced medical technology, including CT scanners, MRI machines, and digital X-ray machines, among others.</p>

<h3>Departments:</h3>
<p><b>New Vision University Hospital has various departments, each of which is dedicated to providing specialized medical care to patients. Some of the departments at the hospital include:</b></p>

<p>Department of Surgery: This department provides specialized surgical care to patients, including general surgery, neurosurgery, plastic surgery, and urology, among others.</p>
<p>Department of Cardiology: This department is dedicated to the diagnosis and treatment of heart diseases and provides various services, including angiography, angioplasty, and pacemaker implantation.</p>

<p>Department of Gynecology and Obstetrics: This department provides specialized care to women, including prenatal care, gynecological exams, and delivery services.</p>

<p>Department of Pediatrics: This department provides medical care to infants, children, and adolescents, including immunizations, well-child exams, and treatment for various illnesses.</p>

<h3>Services:</h3>
<p><b>New Vision University Hospital provides a wide range of medical services to its patients. Some of the services offered at the hospital include:</b></p>
<p>Emergency care: The hospital has a dedicated emergency department that provides urgent medical care to patients.</p>
<p>Outpatient services: The hospital provides various outpatient services, including laboratory tests, imaging services, and diagnostic tests, among others.</p>
<p>Inpatient services: The hospital provides inpatient care to patients who require hospitalization for various medical conditions.</p>

<p>Rehabilitation services: The hospital provides rehabilitation services to patients who have suffered from injuries or illnesses and need help to regain their strength and mobility.</p>

<h3>Mission and Vision:</h3>
<p>New Vision University Hospital's mission is to provide the highest quality medical care to patients and to support medical education and research. The hospital's vision is to be a leading healthcare institution in Georgia and to provide the best possible care to patients.</p>


